Load a theme from a json.

Expected format:
    >>> {
    ...     "Question": {
    ...         "mark_color": "yellow",
    ...         "brackets_color": "normal",
    ...         ...
    ...     },
    ...     "List": {
    ...         "selection_color": "bold_blue",
    ...         "selection_cursor": "->"
    ...     }
    ... }

Color values should be string representing valid blessings.Terminal colors.

